    instructionText: Keep both feet on the floor and focus on shifting weight from
      one foot to the other.
  - exerciseName: Hip Abduction
    exerciseType: 0
    animIndex: 2
    instructionText: Focus on outward, not forward, movement, while standing as straight
      as possible.
  - exerciseName: Leg Lift
    exerciseType: 2
    animIndex: 3
    instructionText: Raise your foot off the ground while staying as balanced as
      you can.
  - exerciseName: Squat
